      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. The S54 straight-six pulls linearly to its 8,000 RPM redline, with a recently serviced VANOS system ensuring optimal cam phasing. The subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the Getrag 6-speed manual offers crisp, short-throw engagement. Riding on a perfectly dialed-in suspension with fresh bushings and a limited-slip differential that locks with surgical precision, this chassis remains incredibly communicative. The exterior is flawless, maintaining its factory depth, while the interior shows zero bolster wear. A collector-grade example for the discerning driver who values mechanical transparency and analog feedback.",
